IRPact_modellierung.agents.companyAgents

Class DefaultProductQualityManipulationScheme

  • java.lang.Object
    • IRPact_modellierung.agents.companyAgents.ProductQualityManipulationScheme
      • IRPact_modellierung.agents.companyAgents.DefaultProductQualityManipulationScheme

  • public class DefaultProductQualityManipulationScheme
extends ProductQualityManipulationScheme
    Since in most models analyzed for deriving the specifications for IRPact the company agent is entirely passive (or non-existent), the DefaultProductQualityManipulationScheme is a ProductQualityManipulationScheme in which the company agent doesn't act (i.e. has an empty manageProductQualities method). It serves to provide an implementation of a ProductQualityManipulationScheme so that instantiation of a CompanyAgent is possible
